</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden czu
                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                                    <add><expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> und</add>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Prager, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            burger <add>und</add> diener, czu reden von etlicher
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<add><expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und</add> kaufflewte und der habe
                            wegen, als <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> diener, her Fridrich von Flednicze
                        </del><app><note><q type="endnote">...</q>Text bricht hier ab.</note></app></ab>
</div>
